</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/a34205891e78.jpg" width="818" height="584" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/98646c364f0d.jpg" width="818" height="584" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/ab2060fa7534.jpg" width="818" height="584" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/9d65c63a76f2.jpg" width="818" height="584" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	横滨捺染 by 滨文样
</h3>
<p>
	滨文样是日本横滨的传统手巾品牌，将一块大的手巾像书一样叠起来，用红色棉线缝合成册，做成了手巾书，大小如同一个口袋本。每一种手巾都是通过横滨捺染的技法制作，是日式传统纹样和配色，很典雅。翻开每一页都是一个主题的不同样式，有很强的故事性。完全拆开后可以用来做桌布或者包裹物品。售价 130 元，<a href="http://s.taobao.com/search?q=滨文样+横滨捺染+文库&js=1&stats_click=search_radio_all%3A1&initiative_id=staobaoz_20151122&ie=utf8" target="_blank">这里是购买链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/5f8c244c546e.jpg" width="750" height="522" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/93dbffb7eedb.jpg" width="750" height="522" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/4d63e48b54ed.jpg" width="750" height="522" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/abf05cbdb9d4.jpg" width="750" height="522" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/12108c6c27fc.jpg" width="750" height="522" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	KANARI collection by&nbsp;<span>KANARI&nbsp;</span> 
</h3>
<p>
	这是来自台湾的设计事务所 KANARI 带来的家用产品系列，包括灯具，时钟和开瓶器。共同点在于每一系列都有金、银、铜三种带有金属感的颜色，线条简明清晰，有古典式的优雅和现代气息。其中，挂钟像套在了几个圆环里，大小圆环的阴影通过灯光投射在墙面上，很有艺术感。目前时钟和开瓶器已可出售，<a href="http://www.studiokanari.com/#!shop/ccnu" target="_blank">这里是购买链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/054f4f11bfc9.jpg" width="1080" height="588" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/f4c2dc76553c.jpg" width="600" height="449" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/2e8bce6186a8.jpg" width="600" height="450" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/263ce8cb127b.jpg" width="600" height="475" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/64e5123add7b.jpg" width="600" height="480" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/726b8ba7ba4c.jpg" width="600" height="474" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	Dorian chair by Rachel Harding
</h3>
<p>
	这是伦敦设计师 Rachel Harding 带来“充气椅”，实际上是将空气充进了可耐力材料里，让椅子可以像花岗岩一样坚固。在高温下，可耐力材料可以变得很柔软，填进空气后有气球的膨胀感，冷却后又重新变成坚固的材料。Rachel Harding 使用了三维建模软件设计了这款充满未来感的椅子，也是对材料的新探索。
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/baf045c7a456.jpg" width="936" height="936" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/1c27774aa1b3.jpg" width="936" height="624" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/547be2121a0f.jpg" width="936" height="624" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/f03d75105361.jpg" width="936" height="624" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/083d9b640ae7.jpg" width="936" height="527" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	Sabbatical Travel Kit by Timbuk2 &amp; Blue Bottle
</h3>
<p>
	这是一款专放咖啡制作器具的帆布包，为那些喜欢自制咖啡且有移动需要的人提供。帆布包的外形方正，近似一个旅行包，打开后可以看到已划分好的格子，可以放置一套咖啡器皿，包括去毛刺的咖啡研磨机、滴水计时器、来自日本的烧水壶、两个珐琅杯等，售价 349 美元，<a href="http://www.timbuk2.com/blue-bottle-sabbatical-travel-kit/581.html?dwvar_581_color=1920&dwvar_581_size=10&utm_source=EEAN-21181&utm_medium=affiliate&utm_campaign=2-223763&utm_content=1449174793&utm_term=skim77721X1528342Xc181123aedcc0e46906fd9d97aa48c21" target="_blank">这里是购买链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/a98bd3df9912.jpg" width="1080" height="637" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/2b5a9970183b.jpg" width="640" height="514" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/1a1fd2603429.jpg" width="465" height="387" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/afc78701858a.jpg" width="465" height="387" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/84be658492fe.jpg" width="465" height="387" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	Bud Light cans by Daniel Triendl
</h3>
<p>
	百威清啤 Bud Light 为了今年的 Mad Decent Block Party，邀请奥地利设计师 Daniel Triendl 设计了一组限量版的易拉罐。罐身可见用油画式的笔触书写的线条或字母，厚重且含有丰富的颜色，显得张扬大胆，契合年轻人。或者使用像素化的图像，在颜色的撞击中带来一种时尚感。<a href="http://danieltriendl.com/Bud-Light-Mad-Decent-Block-Party" target="_blank">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/e9fe1326d3c5.jpg" width="1080" height="607" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201511/53995c330c3e.jpg" width="1080" height="708" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
